B1390: Side Rear Impact Sensor No Response (Driver Side)
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Driver-side rear side-impact sensor has communicated with no response.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" morerows = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
