<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
B1391: Side Rear Impact Sensor Communication Data Invalid (Driver Side)
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Driver-side rear side-impact sensor has communicated with invalid data.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
B1394: Side Rear Impact Sensor Communication Data Inconsistent (Driver Side)
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Driver-side rear side-impact sensor has communicated with inconsistent ID code.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
B1395: Side Rear Impact Sensor No Response (Passenger Side)
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Passenger-side rear side-impact sensor has communicated with no response.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
B1396: Side Rear Impact Sensor Communication Data Invalid (Passenger Side)
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Passenger-side rear side-impact sensor has communicated with invalid data.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
B1399: Side Rear Impact Sensor Communication Data Inconsistent (Passenger Side)
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Passenger-side rear side-impact sensor has communicated with inconsistent ID code.
</ptxt>
</entry>
